Police said that she and her partner had attacked officers, and she had to be handcuffed and arrested.

A police spokesman said that four officers had been sent and added: 'We asked her first to get dressed and leave three times, but her reply was to insult them.

'A further two policeman were called as back up. She still refused to leave and injured two officers in her protests. Her 54-year-old boyfriend then also started making a scene.'

Police overpowered the pair and they were removed in handcuffs - naked - from the sauna.

